lines.content: <!-- Ensures that the label text is never truncated -->
<Label fx:id="course" styleClass="cell_small_label" text="\$course" wrapText="true" minWidth="85" maxWidth="450" />
background-color: #2b2b2b; /* Used in the default.html file */
-fx-text-fill: #d06651 !important; /* The error class should always override the default text-fill style */
/* Empty cells will not have alternating colours */
